Subject: Intro to Metal Working
Description: A basic Q&A session with some show and tell of common tools used by the average metal worker, how they work, and how to use them safely. NO LIVE DEMONSTRATIONS, THINGS WILL CATCH FIRE.  Speakers include:Derek Newland - Track: DIY  - Duration: 1 hour

Subject: Engineering Self Defense
Description: Join us for an open forum of tips and tricks for general self defense, as well as where to get started if you're confused on what to look for in more formal training.  Speakers include:Derek Newland - Track: Life  - Duration: 2 hours
